dct_description_sm: Dibujado por J.P. Morales ; Grabado por Otto Neussel.
Map cut from an original sheet measuring 57.5 x 80 cm. Extensive geographical information. Large engraving depicts allegorical figures, battle scenes, Biblical figures, representative monuments, etc.
Scale also expressed in other units of measurement.
